{"id": 5754, "title": "Ticket #5754: HAD_LIST grows on reconfig", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe member variable in which the HAD state machine stores the HAD_LIST is never cleared; it will therefore grow on each (\"hard\") reconfig.  (A \"hard\" reconfig is rather rarer than it should be because of <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5753\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5753'); return false;\" title=\"HAD improperly ignores some changes to HAD_LIST.\">#5753</a></span>.)\n\n<p>This causes any HAD daemon not also reconfigured to complain:\n\n</p><p></p><div class=\"verbatim\">\n<pre>06/24/16 16:32:08 commandHandler: WARNING: HAD IP list different!\n        me='&lt;128.104.101.142:9000?sock=HAD&gt;,&lt;128.104.101.143:9000?sock=HAD&gt;'\n        other='&lt;128.104.101.142:9000?sock=HAD&gt;,&lt;128.104.101.143:9000?sock=HAD&gt;,&lt;128.104.101.143:9000?sock=HAD&gt;,&lt;128.104.101.142:9000?sock=HAD&gt;'\n</pre></div>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2016-Jun-28 10:05:30 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE REVIEW</strong> looks good.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Jun-28 12:24</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9eb504def4d581517fa735ed849727b519a9e035\">[48679]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5753\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5753'); return false;\" title=\"HAD improperly ignores some changes to HAD_LIST.\">#5753</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5754\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5754'); return false;\" title=\"HAD_LIST grows on reconfig\">#5754</a></span>) Documentation.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Jun-24 16:44</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/75c961e5fce092951604e78fcaad30df73356b73\">[48639]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5754\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5754'); return false;\" title=\"HAD_LIST grows on reconfig\">#5754</a></span>) Clear the HAD <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=StringLists\" title=\"String Lists\">StringLists</a></span> before repeatedly inserting to construct them.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2016-Jun-28 12:43", "status": "resolved", "created": "2016-Jun-24 16:43", "fixed_version": "2016-Jun-24 16:43", "broken_version": "", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "DaemonsCM", "assigned_to": "tlmiller", "derived_from": "", "creator": "tlmiller", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "tlmiller@cs.wisc.edu, johnkn@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}